<p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 10.80pt; margin-top: 0.00pt; margin-bottom: 0.00pt;"><font
	 style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;" face="Arial" size="2">Select
 the object by clicking on it. Move the mouse pointer over the object until
 the mouse pointer changes to a four-headed arrow. Click and drag to the
 desired position.</font></p>
